# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase 1 (prices, fundamentals, filings, valuation) needs NO keys.
# Phase 2 (sentiment) also works out-of-the-box: Reddit, StockTwits and
# news are all hit via free, keyless endpoints. The variables below are
# optional upgrades.
#
# To use: copy this file to ".env" and fill in only what you want.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Reddit User-Agent — Reddit's public .json endpoints reject default
# UAs. Any descriptive string is fine; mention your reddit handle if
# you want to be a good citizen.
REDDIT_USER_AGENT=fire-dashboard/0.1

# X / Twitter — optional, requires a paid API plan. Leave blank to
# keep the X module OFF (fire/sources/x.py silently returns []).
X_BEARER_TOKEN=
